["$","p",null,{"children":["In 2026, sending a paper invoice is like sending a letter via pony express when you have access to high-speed fiber internet. It's charming, but it's dangerously inefficient. For a ",["$","$L8",null,{"href":"/blog/best-invoice-software-for-small-business","className":"text-emerald-600 font-bold underline","children":"small business owner"}],", the transition to online billing isn't just about \"saving trees\"—it's about saving your time, your reputation, and your sanity. This guide provides a deep-dive comparison of the two worlds."]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-8","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-outfit border-b-4 border-emerald-500 pb-2 inline-block","children":"The \"Price\" of Paper"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg","children":"The true cost of a paper invoice isn't just the stamp. It's the cumulative friction of physical logistics."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"p-10 bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-emerald-700 underline decoration-emerald-200 underline-offset-8","children":"Physical Costs"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500 italic","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"• Specialized Paper & Printing (Ink/Toner)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"• Envelopes & Postage"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"• Physical Storage (Filing Cabinets)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"• Shredding & Disposal Services"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"p-10 bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-emerald-700 underline decoration-emerald-200 underline-offset-8","children":"Invisible Costs"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-